com.adyen.core.models.paymentdetails

Class PaymentDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adyen.core.models.paymentdetails.PaymentDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreditCardPaymentDetails, CVCOnlyPaymentDetails, IdealPaymentDetails, SepaDirectDebitPaymentDetails

    public class PaymentDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class for collecting the required PaymentDetails from the shopper to make the payment. This is the generic class that can handle all payment methods. For convenience, several more specific subclasses of this class are provided.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
